::Hot Rod::

He stoped working, and opened a comm.
"Feline, Its Hot Rod. I know we havn't been on good terms since I left
the Alliance, but I'd like to patch things up. And maybe bring back the
feelings we had for each other."

::DrillBit::

He returned to the BlackFortress. He was pleased with how he had been
doing as Commander of the Pack. He then got the message from KitKat.
"KitKat?! This is impossible! Where are you love?"
The voice of his lover brought over welming joy. It also brought
memories, of how he got command. KitKat had been killed by the Alliance.
Megatron tryed to take over, but he had gotton the pack behind him, and
allied with KillFest.

::Epyon::

He was about to tell IR about the battle him and Angel Prime had been
in, but then Prowl and another walked in. He turned to Prowl.
"Hey. What is it?"

::Dollon::

"I was going to ask you two that. Where is everyone?" He replyes to
GoldenEye and Dark Mouse.

::Demolition::

He stands around with the War Machines, out front the CF.
